ids_alerts.rule_msg: (http_inspect) backslash character appears in the path portion of a URI

ids_alerts.rule_msg: PROTOCOL-DNS squid proxy dns PTR record response denial of service attempt
ids_alerts.rule_raw: alert udp $EXTERNAL_NET 53 -> $HOME_NET any ( msg:"PROTOCOL-DNS squid proxy dns PTR record response denial of service attempt"; flow:to_client; content:"|00 0C 00 01|"; content:"|00 0C 00 01|",within 4,distance 2; content:"|00 01 00|",within 3,distance 4; metadata:policy max-detect-ips drop; service:dns; reference:bugtraq,12551; reference:cve,2005-0446; classtype:attempted-dos; sid:17484; rev:10; )
